item.title: CVE-2023-36492|2023-09-05T09:09:44.818Z -- shirasagi%20project -- shirasagi
item.description: Reflected cross-site scripting vulnerability in SHIRASAGI prior to v1.18.0 allows a remote unauthenticated attacker to execute an arbitrary script on the web browser of the user who is logging in to the product.
